neg_text:
-Stale cigarette smell in the room;
-Air conditioning system was switched off centrally so I couldn't turn it on;
-The fridge was barely working;
-The room was completely out dated with many dings in the walls, damaged power outlet, staines on the carpet , torn bedding...
-The breakfast selection and quality was average.

pos_text:
Convenient location near the city center, quiet room facing the courtyard;
friendly, courteous staff,
Excellent cuisine in the hotel's own restaurant, sumptuous breakfast that goes beyond "continental"

neg_text:
- worn out;
